docs.text: Austin Healy Club Website For this project, Eesha and I worked on the 'About Page' for the Austin Healey Club of Minnesota. docs.text: Structured Authoring with Dita For my Dita project, I decided to create a recipe on how to create Spicy Margaritas. Ever since I turned 21 and the start of COVID, I have been obsessed with making cocktails at home and I learned how to make margaritas and spicy margaritas.
